                     <interp inst="t18250113-106-off552" type="offenceSubcategory" value="animalTheft"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18250113-106-cd553" type="crimeDate">22d of December</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18250113-106-off552 t18250113-106-cd553"></join>, a hamper, value 3 s., and nine geese, value 25 s.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               <persName id="t18250113-106-victim573" type="victimName">
                  John 
                  Bloomfield
               <interp inst="t18250113-106-victim573" type="surname" value="Bloomfield"></interp>
